Class RewardVendor

  • java.lang.Object
    • decoworld.model.world.entities.WorldEntity

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    HasCollision, HasMouseOver, HasPhysicsBox, HasLocation, HasRotation, WorldItem, HasItemLabel, HasWorldItemEvent

    public class RewardVendor
extends Building

    This class stores all information such as its ID, coordinate and maps as a RewardVendor building object existing in the world. The building and a map inside of it is created based on the information on this class. The preset map are set on a class. Therefore, more than one instance of building can be created, but each of the buildings have exactly same exterior and interior image.
